1. Write ChangeLog entry.

2. make dist, check that it builds and installs correctly.

3. git commit

4. git tag -s Release_X.Y.Z

5. Git commit (git status, git add all modified files, git commit)

6. git tag -s Release_X.Y.Z

7. git push, git push --tags

8. Sign (gpg -b) and upload dist tarball 
   (sftp larsl@dl.sv.nongnu.org:/releases/ll-plugins).

9. Generate new API documentation, upload it, update the redirect page.

10. Update webpages.

11. Announce on http://freshmeat.net and any relevant mailing lists.
